{"tid":711022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳孫波賣改造遼寧艦資料予CIA","createTime":"2018-06-21T08:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:20:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0e16a2c7cd66fb3bea82d9d310dad70f0e807924","tid":711022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180621/20426712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20426712&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=adfe1456\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20426712&h=59cb358b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180621/20426712</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月21日 <br />\n<br />\n傳孫波賣改造遼寧艦資料予CIA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180621/large/a2305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180621%2Flarge%2Fa2305a.gif&h=7a1b80a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中船重工公開的圖片，中間的疑是新國產航母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地軍事巨企中國船舶重工集團（簡稱中船重工）總經理孫波涉嚴重違法違紀落馬被中紀委調查，當局無披露箇中底蘊。內地網絡傳言四起，有指「孫波把遼寧艦全部改造資料賣給美國中情局（CIA）」；也有指孫波落馬和航母無關，是他個人違法違紀問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二艘航母圖疑曝光<br />\n<br />\n孫波落馬後，有內地軍事網即傳他因向CIA出賣遼寧艦改造的資料，成了美國間諜而出事；網絡熱傳一時，但無法求證；有網民引述匿名軍事專家稱，航母是國家戰略武器裝備，每一個造船步驟都受到嚴格審查和管理，不太可能出現個人受賄後在某環節偷工減料、私相授受問題。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中船重工昨在官方微信發佈公司董事長胡問鳴視察有「中國航母搖籃」之稱、位於湖北武漢的中國艦船研究設計中心並出席會議的消息，配發圖片暗藏重大玄機，圖片出現三艘航母領航的大型艦艇編隊，一艘相信是遼寧艦，一艘是正在海試的首艘國產航母。<br />\n<br />\n而位居中央的航母體形更大，且採用平直甲板設計，外界認為可能是傳聞中的第二艘國產航母，採用彈射起飛。內地軍事專家宋忠平估計，新航母噸位至少8萬噸以上，採用蒸汽彈射或電磁彈射，與美軍最新入役的福特級核動力航母看齊。胡問鳴在會上對部下展示反腐決心。<br />\n<br />\n環球網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n金正恩結束訪華　稱無核化達共識<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n狗肉節今開鑼　玉林變態食客貴婦狗照吃"},{"pid":"da6853fd3e1dd59dc602626b2b3ec08775d75b26","tid":711022,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"美國佬係咪同佢講做間諜就派綠卡俾佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eaba88bcf3abaf326aca1a65ab6f0cdadc13d0","tid":711022,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257f27b465d6d68ba1e8c98b66a20b9bf25169c1","tid":711022,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55eaba88bcf3abaf326aca1a65ab6f0cdadc13d0","tid":711022,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"當睇套笑片咁上下"},{"pid":"e3f675bbd57d526566a2276ca881ccf415076557","tid":711022,"uid":5267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3260cd000c7da584b24cfb36fe4353f6e711aa2f","tid":711022,"uid":186268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44d4c39e6b19f01ccddff4fe265bd18427027faa","tid":711022,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55eaba88bcf3abaf326aca1a65ab6f0cdadc13d0","tid":711022,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:35:33.000Z","msg":"得個知字啫"},{"pid":"99720621cf498466a107fea498ad27143c4c45f3","tid":711022,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"海試？<img src=\"/assets/fa